## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in opinion pieces. The analysis primarily relies on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of the issue. Additionally, the perspectives included are predominantly from Western sources, which may not fully represent the views of all demographic groups within the U.S. Further research could include primary data collection through surveys or interviews with American sports fans.